text: Azizul Haq Mollah is a Bangladesh Nationalist Party politician and the former Member of Parliament of Bogra-4. ==Career== Mollah was elected to parliament from Bogra-4 as a Bangladesh Nationalist Party candidate in 1991. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Nationalist Party politicians Category:1993 deaths Category:5th Jatiya Sangsad members
title: Azizul Haq Mollah
